@identityBaseUrl = http://localhost:5001
@expenseBaseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@apiVersion = 1.0

###
# Bu dosya REST Client extension ile kullanilmak uzere hazirlandi.
# On kosullar:
# 1. `docker compose up -d` ile PostgreSQL, RabbitMQ ve Ollama'yi kaldir.
# 2. VS Code icinden `Debug SourceEx APIs` compound launch config'ini baslat.
# 3. Sirayla request'leri calistir.
###

### Identity health check
GET {{identityBaseUrl}}/health/live

### Expense API health check
GET {{expenseBaseUrl}}/health/live

### Employee kullanicisi ile login ol ve token al
# @name employeeLogin
POST {{identityBaseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userNameOrEmail": "employee-001",
  "password": "Passw0rd!"
}

### Employee token ile identity serviste current user kontrol et
GET {{identityBaseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeLogin.response.body.accessToken}}

### Employee token ile expense API'de claim aktarimini kontrol et
GET {{expenseBaseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeLogin.response.body.accessToken}}

### Employee olarak yeni expense olustur
# @name createExpense
POST {{expenseBaseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeLogin.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1499.99,
  "currency": "TRY",
  "description": "Conference travel for security workshop"
}

### Olusan expense kaydini employee token ile goruntule
GET {{expenseBaseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/expenses/{{createExpense.response.body.expenseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{employeeLogin.response.body.accessToken}}

### Manager kullanicisi ile login ol
# @name managerLogin
POST {{identityBaseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userNameOrEmail": "manager-001",
  "password": "Passw0rd!"
}

### Manager token ile expense approval akisini tetikle
POST {{expenseBaseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/expenses/{{createExpense.response.body.expenseId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{managerLogin.response.body.accessToken}}

### Expense durumunu approval sonrasinda tekrar kontrol et
GET {{expenseBaseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/expenses/{{createExpense.response.body.expenseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{managerLogin.response.body.accessToken}}

### Refresh token akisini test et
# @name refreshManagerToken
POST {{identityBaseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{managerLogin.response.body.refreshToken}}"
}

### Refresh sonrasinda manager profilini yeni access token ile tekrar cek
GET {{identityBaseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{refreshManagerToken.response.body.accessToken}}
